{
  "page": "Street of Silver",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Street of Silver</b> is a street in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> where gamblers gather.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Street_of_Silver&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Street_of_Silver&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jacelyn_Bywater\" title=\"Jacelyn Bywater\">Jacelyn Bywater</a> reports to <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> that <a href=\"/index.php/Timett\" title=\"Timett\">Timett</a> killed a <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wineseller</a>'s son at a <a href=\"/index.php/Gambling\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Gambling\">gambling</a> den on the Street of Silver.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">